<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<title>ạnạ mʿạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạnạ mʿạk ḍạmn slạmy ạnạ mʿạk ḍạmn frḥy

[V2]
 ạnạ mʿạk ḍạmn njạḥy ʿmr mạ ywm yḍʿf qlby

[V3]
 1- mhmạ dẖạdt hmwmy mhmạ dqt ạlạm ḥbk dwạʾ lrwḥy wbtmlạny bslạm

[V4]
 dh ạnt ạlrb ạlly sạndny mạlyny bạlạmạn

[V5]
 2- mhmạ ʿdwy ḍạyqny mhmạ ạlḥrwb tzyd ạnt ạlhy wḥạrsny wmʿạk ḥyạty ạkyd

[V6]
 dh ạnt ạlrb ạlly sạndny wbtkẖlyny sʿyd

[V7]
 3- mhmạ ạlạyạm tkẖwny wtʿạndny ạlẓrwf wʿdk lyạ yṭmny wbynzʿ mny ạlkẖwf

[V8]
 dh ạnt ạlrb ạlly sạndny wạnt ạbwyạ ạlʿṭwf

[V9]
 4- wạtẖq fyk tgẖyrny wbtsẖklny ạydyk wfy ḍʿfy btklmny ʿlsẖạn ạnạ ạbn lyk

[V10]
 dh ạnt ạlrb ạlly sạndny btʿlmny ạkẖḍʿ lyk</lyrics>
</song>